  <body>
    <p>The <xref keyref="glossentry_quick-assist"><term>Quick Assist</term> support</xref> helps you
      to rapidly access search and refactoring actions. If one or more actions are available in the
      current context, they are accessible via a yellow bulb icon (<image
        href="../img/QuickAssist16.png"/>) placed at the current line in the stripe on the left side
      of the editor. Also, you can invoke the <term>Quick Assist</term> menu by using the
          <uicontrol><shortcut>Alt + 1</shortcut></uicontrol> (<uicontrol><shortcut>Meta + Alt +
          1</shortcut></uicontrol> on Mac OS X) keyboard shortcuts.</p>
